import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row';

function GridComplexExample() {
  return (

    <Form>
      <Row className="mb-3">
        <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridEmail">
          <Form.Label>Username</Form.Label>
          <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Username" />
        </Form.Group>
      </Row>

      <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formGridAddress1">
        <Form.Label>Address</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control placeholder="1234 Main St" />
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formGridAddress2">
        <Form.Label>Address 2</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control placeholder="Apartment, studio, or floor" />
      </Form.Group>

      <Row className="mb-3">

        <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
          <Form.Label>State</Form.Label>
          <Form.Select defaultValue="Choose...">
            <option>Choose...</option>
            <option>...</option>
          </Form.Select>
        </Form.Group>

        <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridZip">
          <Form.Label>Zip</Form.Label>
          <Form.Control />
        </Form.Group>
      </Row>

      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Restlessness" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Uncontrollable feelings of worry" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Increased irritabilityt" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Difficulty concentrating" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Sleep difficulties" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Feeling very sad, hopeless or worried. Children and adolescents with depression may be irritable rather than sad" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Low Energy" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Having thoughts of self-harm or suicide" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Being easily irritated or frustrated." />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Eating too much or too little, which may result in weight gain or weight loss" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Experiencing physical issues like headache, stomachache or sexual dysfunction" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Having the urge to avoid things that trigger anxiety" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Having difficulty controlling worry" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Having trouble sleeping" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Having an increased heart rate" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Having a sense of impending danger, panic or doom" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" id="formGridCheckbox">
        <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Trouble concentrating or thinking about anything other than the present worry" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
        Submit
      </Button>
    </Form>

  );
}

export default GridComplexExample;
